data.title: Abbie Cornish currently has no agent, publicist or stylist
data.meta_description: With no agent, no publicist and no stylist these days (just my manager Michael Lazo) it seems like Im now running my own advertising campaigns too. What am I advertising here you ask? I dont know... free hair cuts by me, freedom, and this dress I bought for $25 on Amazon 😹…
